text: Diadelia nervulata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fairmaire in 1903.BioLib.cz - Diadelia nervulata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==Subspecies== * Diadelia nervulata nervulata Fairmaire, 1903 * Diadelia nervulata propinqua Breuning, 1940 ==References== Category:Diadelia Category:Beetles described in 1903
